Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.50,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找吧  收集梦想的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.57,0:00:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无奈也能感受到此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表看起来更单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.35,0:00:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法坦诚表达心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.99,0:00:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把想说的话收藏在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.26,0:00:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今更不能说出幼稚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.64,0:00:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好说时间能解决一切 却怕无人能懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.51,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天24小时我都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是司空见惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.19,0:01:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是嘲笑着匆匆而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.43,0:01:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其执着回忆 不如寻找现在的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只虫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妖化的那段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.85,0:02:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑制了犬夜叉的妖怪之血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底铁碎牙不过是狗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时  铁碎牙被折断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而唤醒了犬夜叉的妖怪之血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.87,0:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  曾经觉醒的妖怪之血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.41,0:02:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会因自卫的本能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而再一次妖化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以绝对不能放开铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为\N只要生命受到威胁的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体就会再起变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再度妖化的时候  我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的这爪子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会把你撕成碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.60,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗  刀刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你差不多也该来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第53话 父亲的宿敌龙骨精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉那家伙跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇你完全想不到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.01,0:03:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉应该是想让铁碎牙变轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是在某处修行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不觉得犬夜叉会这么老实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  只能一个不漏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找找每个可能的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.47,0:04:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太想告诉大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉现在非常的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.61,0:04:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得让他\N独自一人会比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.94,0:04:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有静静的等待  我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.88,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.16,0:04:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你太失望了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.86,0:04:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被铁碎牙的重量耍得团团转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆!所以我才希望你\N教我变轻的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.43,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己努力找呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很急耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.94,0:04:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再妖化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法随心所欲使用铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会让那种杂鱼妖怪\N逼的走投无路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得毫无道理可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷  您没事真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家明明很担心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来这里避难的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷  你隐瞒的真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.73,0:05:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少装蒜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.73,0:05:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是铁碎牙与我的妖化的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从戈薇那里听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.50,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙是为了封印\N我的妖怪之血而打造的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明交代她要守口如瓶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道了  要是没有变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀还是会被抢走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能将铁碎牙挥舞自如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  你已经深刻体验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不敢妖化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.97,0:06:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.34,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  去杀龙骨精吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙骨精?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.72,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…你是说龙骨精?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙骨精这家伙  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你父亲经过一番缠斗之后\N封印住的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你觉得新的铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.01,0:06:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为锻入刀中的你的牙齿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.74,0:07:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就比不上父亲的强悍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果砍死和老爸战斗过的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等于超越了老爸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算您说要斩杀它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您记住  犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您只要贯穿在封印状态之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的龙骨精的心脏就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  不是跟他打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是连令尊好不容易封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是无法彻底消灭的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.11,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种好像骗人的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您再这么罗哩叭嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不带路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对谁用这种口气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗?我吗?\N不是  别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很有趣吗  神无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  神乐  悟心鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽郎丸  影郎丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:08:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能宰掉犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让他试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫龙骨精的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷  还没到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一下子就可以看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么烂路嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷知道他在哪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他一定拿着铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑去老爷爷那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪  在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉啊  他跑去龙骨精之谷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙骨精之谷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷  就是那里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…龙骨精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.23,0:10:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  而那个封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊的爪子刺进去的部位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是龙骨精的心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.71,0:10:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刀刀斋爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有那种方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早一点告诉他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太简单啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这么轻松就让他学会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.10,0:10:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就不会有这种体认了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犬夜叉已经相当痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.74,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在痛苦与烦恼的煎熬之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.78,0:10:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才跑去找爷爷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对手是强盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他毕竟对人类下了手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才告诉他不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能毫不在乎对人类下手的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有资格拥有铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落  你想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印的爪子被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.69,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙骨精  在那里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是将你封印住的\N那可恨的人的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的找他算帐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.63,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧  犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么梦话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我就对偷偷摸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.27,0:12:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷袭被封印的家伙\N的方式很不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不直接砍了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙不就无法变轻了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.88,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼…你想砍了我龙骨精?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.12,0:13:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点子还不坏  就陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩玩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逞强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍眼的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙骨精这家伙还挺行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.95,0:14:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙要收拾犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.72,0:14:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是轻而易举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的余兴节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我好好期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是傀儡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.96,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不配让我暖身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.23,0:14:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才从一开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以奈落为目标吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.37,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该能让我有所期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好  龙骨精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股猛烈的妖气是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.86,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷  犬夜叉他该不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.26,0:15:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那呆子居然让龙骨精觉醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么强烈的妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次遇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.74,0:15:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉在和这种对手战斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.71,0:15:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也过去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.15,0:15:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是个不好的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧  小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就好好陪你玩一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然这么大言不惭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸爪子的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要刺中那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙就能变轻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙…砍不下去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.93,0:16:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.33,0:16:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体可是比钢铁更硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷  这还是太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不过刚开始而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这龙骨精连令尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.97,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都费了好大的劲才封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不只是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊就是因为和龙骨精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.38,0:17:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战时所受的伤才会身亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经挂了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那家伙的儿子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想用那把钝刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来报杀父之仇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不凑巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得老爹长什么样子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今哪有什么仇不仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.91,0:17:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.94,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是靠着令尊\N遗留的铁碎牙到现在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个不孝子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想逃了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的铁碎牙之所以沉重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为锻入刀中的我的牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比不上老爸的牙那么强韧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  打倒龙骨精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能超越老爸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.77,0:18:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.97,0:18:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么\N龙骨精的封印会被解开呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.51,0:18:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.41,0:18:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这下子变的很麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是龙骨精再度出来作乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个武藏国都会变成焦土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是这么厉害的妖怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.92,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何才能打败那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打倒苏醒的龙骨精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方法只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.67,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了爆流破别无它法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆流破…那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是铁碎牙的奥义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.04,0:19:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说它是奥义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是比“风之伤”更厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.51,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么“风之伤”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是初学者的招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉别说是风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连挥动铁碎牙都很吃力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况是奥义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.47,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又丢下犬夜叉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.57,0:20:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连玩弄的价值都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没办法解消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你父亲封印的怨气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.85,0:20:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种钝刀根本伤不了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能放开铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为性命垂危的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉就会妖化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用…死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.97,0:21:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉没有拿着铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.62,0:22:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.87,0:22:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了真正重要的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.98,0:22:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能舍弃其他一切就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.22,0:22:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而现实却是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.60,0:22:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的时刻只要随时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.50,0:22:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.00,0:23:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海浮现你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.68,0:23:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-但愿直到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.05,0:23:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远沉睡的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.56,0:23:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.97,0:23:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不止息存在我心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.99,0:23:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖化成妖怪的犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.16,0:23:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再待在这里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.32,0:23:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也许会一起被卷入战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  刀刀斋爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.43,0:23:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我们撤退?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.16,0:23:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能丢下犬夜叉不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.57,0:24:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了独自一人得到真正的强悍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.67,0:24:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉卯足了全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.94,0:24:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时  铁碎牙开始鼓动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.81,0:24:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.24,0:24:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙的奥义 爆流破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.48,0:24:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待



